works.description: Bugatti, which is known as a symbol of European car manufacturing, especially racing cars, has introduced one innovative and iconic design after the other, such as the Porcelain Bugatti which we covered recently. This time, a rare 1925 Type 35 racing car went under the hammer for $692,789 at the 2011 Goodwood Festival of Speed, which had modern-day greats like Lewis Hamilton in attendance.
